title: Grand Theft Autumn (Where Is Your Boy)

description:
Changes are mainly after the second chorus where Wentz in the original audio is clearly playing a more pronounced bass line than just the roots, the "he won't find out section" it is a very fun little riff, and for someone listening to the song for bass, it is very obvious. I also altered the intro riff, later repeated, to 16th notes, which is again, matched in the audio of the song recording, and is meant to support the guitar doing the same thing.
(via editor)
